{"tid":1292077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日日跳樓自殺 日日車禍死人","createTime":"2019-07-07T06:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:58:46.000Z","uid":274055,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b9176e3f706c894e91674acf6fcf64c4e9a941","tid":1292077,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"香港好似一個悲情城市，日日都有人跳樓或用其他方式自殺 ，尤其最近多咗好多誘因。<br />\n仲有日日車禍死人，唔係撞死市區途人就係死車上嘅人（尤其電單車手）。<br />\n呢兩大非自然死法一般都冇兇案等咁受關注，大衆都習以爲常，冇得到正視及解決，以致爲咗已死嘅人爭一口氣都補唔返。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我哋係咪要日日拜呢啲當日死嘅人，去引起社會關注，搵出根源？</strong><br />\n<br />\n大家可以搜集下每日有幾多個 就知道有幾嚴重：<br />\n今日 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190707/59796884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190707%2F59796884&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=5e8064c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190707%2F59796884&h=28cf1844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190707/59796884</a>"},{"pid":"a9f688319f36c5810e35be1f53f825391cf6687d","tid":1292077,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"更正：<br />\n<br />\n2018年交通意外死左135人（行人佔64個），所以平均每2.7日死一個。全年嚴重受傷1840人，平均每日重傷5人先係日日有。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/statistics/traffic_report_2018_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fstatistics%2Ftraffic_report_2018_tc.pdf&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=aa225388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/statistics/traffic_report_2018_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年自殺死916人，所以平均每日死2.5人，真係日日死人。<br />\n而且近期已經超過平均數。每日個案：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=fa62395a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<br />\n至今已有10宗跟返送中相關的企圖自殺：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JxhfFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JxhfFw&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=68d36441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JxhfFw</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Nz1naS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Nz1naS&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=aabfbd3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Nz1naS</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NxAvIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NxAvIk&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=077df018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NxAvIk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NtevOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NtevOU&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=a7de491c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NtevOU</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ntq4Wn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ntq4Wn&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=a4779688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ntq4Wn</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LxsQr2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LxsQr2&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=ff762de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LxsQr2</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XbgaIr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XbgaIr&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=66d29324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XbgaIr</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FD14Wc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FD14Wc&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3